    "body": "same as https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/issues/21153\r\nBasically we prevent DOS by using a mechanism called gas.\r\nEach operation on the evm costs gas. If you run a infinite loop within a normal transaction the gas mechanism would prevent the DOS. However you are trying to run the operation directly on the evm which means you surpass the safety mechanism",
